Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.61,0:00:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maurer, you haven't been\Ntaking a bath, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.65,0:00:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised, when I moved\Nto the desk next to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.70,0:00:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,that you'd take one every other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.62,0:00:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a visitor\Nin the reception office.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home,\Nso make your own tea, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A visitor? At this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't had a bath, either.\NHe smells almost as bad as you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.72,0:00:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Upsy daisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And whose fault is it that\NI haven't been able to take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.65,0:00:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't realize that she's able to\Nmake a living at this paper
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,with no future,\Nthanks to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.24,0:00:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... My name is Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask for your assistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... He really is filthy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.38,0:01:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so you're a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.09,0:01:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look like one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.30,0:01:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, Doctor,\Nis this what you're trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.31,0:01:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The next target of the person\Nwho's been killing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,middle-aged couples\Nthroughout Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is here in Heidelberg?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That couple is fostering a young girl,\Nand when that girl turns 20,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the killer will come to take her away...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And when he does, the foster parents\Nare sure to be killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have no idea\Nwho that girl or her foster parents are,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,or where they live...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's not delusional,\NI don't know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a joke. Please believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even the gossip rags\Nwould write up that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here\Nto get you to write it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,After those twins\Nslipped out of the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,there is at least\Na 6-month blank period
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,before the brother showed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.61,0:02:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that,\Nafter leaving the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,those twins came to\NHeidelberg together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.95,0:02:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And the two were raised by\Nthe girl's current foster parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But the brother ran away from here\Nafter a short period,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving his sister behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.67,0:02:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you write a novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,'Course it probably won't sell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It is possible that there is\Na missing person's report out on the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And there might even be\Na newspaper article about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me check the newspapers\Nfrom nine years ago! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We mustn't allow\Nany more people to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The president has a thing against\Ncomputerization, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,These are smaller versions of the daily newspapers, and manuscript files.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And these are files\Nof cancelled stories and raw data.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the Japanese bow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't have the time\Nto spend on silly stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.03,0:03:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and leave\Nwhen you're satisfied!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Every once in a while,\NI get a nut case like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please let me find something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.\NYou're looking well, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fainting like that...\NYou startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you really didn't like\Nthe boy we hooked you up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I just suddenly felt bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to apologize to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind.\NYou don't have to worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That Otto... When I talked to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I found out that he's not\Nyour "prince on a white horse."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he didn't send you\Nany email message.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that you fainted\Nbecause you saw that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I only saw him for a second,\Nso I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your impression of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt very nostalgic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't explain it well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You needn't force yourself, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolute evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to put it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it felt just like\Nwhen I had that nightmare...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"Absolute evil"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beginning to sound religious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't go to a church...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it seems to me that everything will be cleared up if I see that person again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel that you will regain\Nthe memory you've lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one means you may be\Nable to employ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think you should let that\Nbe a burden on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about your future\Nwithout stressing, is also important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just work up a sweat playing sports,\Nand your insecurities should disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maurer, pull another all-nighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,were you the one who let that guy use the file room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I asked him\Nwhat he was doing there
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and he said\Nyou had given him permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean he's still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! It's about time you... Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right? Hey! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I always have breakfast here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife left me, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always so busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When I finally realized it, my wife had gone back to her parents with our daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever thought about\Nbringing your wife home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one who walked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I go to get her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you seem to regret\Nbeing so occupied with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Work is most important to a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Any wife who cannot understand that\Nis welcome to leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. It was none of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NIt's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh... One more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You smoke too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I say that as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you it's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit saying the same thing\Nmy wife said!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife was worried\Nabout your health, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina's birthday present?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I finally finished it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Her sweaters used to be\Nthis tiny before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, are you really going to tell her
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that she's not really our daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't we leave it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to tell her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina is our daughter, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy... am I hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Gaitel may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:11:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tomorrow, your birthday, let's meet at\NHeidelberg Castle at 7:00 PM."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,at Heidelberg Castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so busy, but here I am staring at\Na mountain of papers with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time you gave up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If... it's just a thought, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to go to get my wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think she'd come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you quit smoking, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,11-year-old boy disappears...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:12:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It is possible that he was kidnapped, but there has been no word from a kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,16 Necker Street...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone named Fortner has filled out\Na missing person's report!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The raw data should be\Nin here somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.55,0:12:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that killer would
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,come to take his sister away\Nwhen she turned 20, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If the boy in this article\Nis her brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! His birth date is printed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the 20th birthday\Nof those twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hello, Dad? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I just finished work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to meet up with a friend\Nthen I'll be coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... At Heidelberg Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:13:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom is making preparations\Nfor a birthday party, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. She says she's going to meet\Na friend before coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina's all grown up, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe this will help me to remember things...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to know...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who I really am.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, what do you intend to do if\Nthe twin girl is at the Fortners' home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the case,\Nthat family is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.13,0:13:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I will contact the police\Nand ask for protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think the police will\Ndo anything just from your reasoning?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing has happened yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be too late\Nafter something happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all in your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the four murder cases, I myself went to the crime scene in Cologne.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There was something different\Nabout that scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I sensed no purpose, no greed, no bitterness...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like someone simply ended\Nthese people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell just by looking\Nat the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.59,0:14:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that a kid\Nwho wasn't even 20, did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But do you think a youngster could kill\Nthose people without feeling any emotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't something done by a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was something bigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Bigger... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't find the right words\Nto describe this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have to describe it,\Nit's trite, but that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the Devil's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If that killer were to appear before me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I would kill him without a pause.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,16 Necker Street...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!\NSorry to call on you so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to bother you.\NI'm Maurer of the Heidelberg Post.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What would a newspaper\Nreporter be wanting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I'd like to ask you\Nsome questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's regarding this missing persons report\Nthat you filed in 1986...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You can forget about that matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Could you please talk to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:15:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have a girl living with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.11,0:16:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The twin sister of\Nthe boy who disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They had a birthday cake prepared...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You took in a pair of twins\Nnine years ago, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl still lives with you,\Ndoesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We have raised her\Nas our true daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't make waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You took in a pair of twins\Nnine years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy had surgical scars\Non his head
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and the girl had amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Fortner, you must contact\Nthe police at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your lives, and your daughter's,\Nare in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let us see your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She is out at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,At Heidelberg Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she was going\Nto meet a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me use your car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! We must\Nnotify the police first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have the time\Nto explain things to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the key, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call them from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said earlier,\Nhe's a terrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better not die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Maurer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll quit smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll follow the quack's advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.18,0:17:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife will be happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how should I explain\Nthis to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Our daughter... Is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me use your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What has happened to our daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The phone line's been cut...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna... Please be safe... Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way past time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that message was a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to... wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was asked to make sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you waited here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to wait...\NDon't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was told!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna... No, you're Nina Fortner,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dr. Tenma. I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna... Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. You must go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You... Are you...\Nmy prince on a white horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't butt in... Don't butt in, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gotta wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If she doesn't, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't get paid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.30,0:20:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He said no one would come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm amazed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I need something to tie him up with!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:20:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who asked you to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When did he say he was coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.04,0:21:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He just said he would come here after doing something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... your home...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to hurry back to your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to hurry, Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.23,0:21:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.61,0:21:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get loose...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.80,0:21:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:22:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.30,0:22:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.43,0:22:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, when you were\Nbrought into my hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you were Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And your brother's name was Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.25,0:22:36.88,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And slowly, you come to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:44.30,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It's all as it should be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.18,0:22:53.73,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You can only do so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.90,0:22:59.32,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If you're game enough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.78,0:23:07.12,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}You could place your trust in me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:16.21,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For the love of life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.34,0:23:21.55,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}There's a trade off
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:28.30,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We could lose it all
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:33.23,ED-ENG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But we'll go down fighting
